<interface:HTMLContainer xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:repository="http://general_server.org/xmlnamespaces/repository/2006" title="LibXML2r">
  <h2>ALTERATIONS</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>xml:hardlink</li>
    <li>xml:deviation</li>
    <li>no default document-order sorting. use database:document-order(node-set) @data-type=number for this</li>
    <li>AXIS_NAME is the default axis for non-namespace steps, e.g. /Server/</li>
    <li>C string literal escaping is introduced to XSL string literals, e.g. 'test'quote' can be written 'test\'quote'</li>
  </ul>
  
  <h2>NEW AXIS</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>name</li>
    <li>parent-route</li>
    <li>parent-natural</li>
    <li>hardlink</li>
    <li>top</li>
    <li>parents</li>
    <li>ancestors</li>
    <li>ancestors-or-self</li>
    <li>descendant-natural</li>
  </ul>
  
  <h2>NEW GRAMMAR</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>~Class name</li>
    <li>^x id(x)</li>
    <li>`x session:node-set(x)</li>
  </ul>
</interface:HTMLContainer>
